  ### Create a dotfile
  ```
  touch .bashrc
  ```

  ### Refresh bash to see changes
  ```
  source ~/.bashrc
  ```

  ### Aliases
  ```
  alias c="clear"
  alias ll="ls -lha"
  alias gs="git status"
  alias ga="git add"
  alias gc="git commit -m"
  # Then running *c* in your terminal will be the same as running *clear*, and so on
  ```
  ### Functions
